      <url>/2020/02/14/Hexo%E4%B8%8Emarkdown%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>使用博客，首先要打开命令行，切换到博客文件夹下。</p><p>如何新建文章？</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new 文章标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如何上传修改后的博客？</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><p>如何打出上下角标？</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">上标：A（小于号）sup（大于号）2（小于号）&#x2F;sup（大于号）</span><br><span class="line">下标：sup换成sub</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;&#x2F;用markdown语法的~A...这个会报错，原因我也不清楚</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其他的想到再补充</p>]]></content>
      
      
